03:53.191 --> 03:55.193
-We're the Friends.
-We're the Friend family.

03:55.276 --> 03:57.654
That's our-- Our last name is Friend,
we're the Friend family.

03:57.737 --> 03:59.781
We're friends, too,
but we're also the Friend family.

03:59.864 --> 04:00.698
Yeah.

04:00.782 --> 04:02.867
And what do you wanna say about us, babe?

04:03.785 --> 04:04.953
I don't know, we're...

04:05.787 --> 04:07.038
Uh, we're fun.

