always wants to make you laugh.

04:28.935 --> 04:30.853
I love that about her.
She's a great mom.

04:31.145 --> 04:32.730
I want the yellow!

04:32.814 --> 04:33.690
Oh...

04:33.773 --> 04:35.942
<i>She's, uh... She's pretty amazing.</i>

04:36.317 --> 04:37.568
She's got amazing eyes.

