08:26.797 --> 08:27.715
Oh, yeah.

08:27.798 --> 08:30.218
I think I can make this easier to use.

08:30.301 --> 08:33.513
I do like the rack, but I think
we can fix it so that it's easier to use.

08:33.596 --> 08:35.765
- Oh, my God!

08:35.848 --> 08:37.391
-Was that planned
- Please be careful!

08:37.475 --> 08:39.644
- Oh, my God.
