It's either too small or too big.

09:00.706 --> 09:01.999
But Marie, I'll tell you...

09:02.083 --> 09:03.793
-Want my mom.
-Okay, I'm coming.

09:03.876 --> 09:05.920
- Mommy! Mommy!
- Yes, I hear you.

