09:14.387 --> 09:15.429
Yes, yes, um...

09:15.763 --> 09:18.140
I want to sit on the floor with you.

09:18.224 --> 09:19.684
You can sit-- Okay.

09:20.059 --> 09:22.019
KonMari chair.

09:26.983 --> 09:28.359
So both of you work?

09:28.442 --> 09:29.485
He mostly works.

09:29.569 --> 09:32.697
I teach Intercultural Communication,
a few days a week,

09:32.822 --> 09:34.782
